Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Il mio nome è Shinichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Sono un detective liceale\Nfamoso in tutto il Giappone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma a causa del veleno di una banda criminale
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,sono diventato Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.17,0:00:10.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Non importa se sono piccolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:12.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho la mente di un brillante detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Risolvo casi impossibili \Nanche per gli adulti!
